cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.SI 

This paper is primarily focused on the analysis of regularized deep neural networks, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and neural networks (cs.NE). The paper also discusses the use of ReLU activation functions (cs.CV) and convex optimization techniques (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper's focus on analyzing the structure of hidden layers in deep neural networks could also fall under the category of computational complexity (cs.SI).
